quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,94,"Dájúdájú (Allāhu) mọ̀ wọ́n. Ó sì ka òǹkà wọn tààrà."
  19,95,"Gbogbo wọn yó sì wá bá A ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde ní ìkọ̀ọ̀kan."
  19,96,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, Àjọkẹ́-ayé yóò fi ìfẹ́ sáààrin wọn."
  20,76,"(Ohun ni) àwọn Ọgbà ìdẹ̀ra gbére tí àwọn odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ìyẹn sì ni ẹ̀san fún ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣàfọ̀mọ́ (iṣẹ́ rẹ̀).”"
  20,77,"Àti pé dájúdájú A ti fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí (Ànábì) Mūsā báyìí pé: “Mú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi rìn ní òru. Fi (ọ̀pá rẹ) na omi fún wọn (kí ó di) ojú ọ̀nà gbígbẹ kan nínú omi òkun.{1} O ò níí bẹ̀rù àlébá, o ò sì níí páyà (ìtẹ̀rì sínú omi òkun).”.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:50.]
  20,78,"Fir‘aon sì tẹ̀lé wọn pẹ̀lú àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀. Ohun tí ó bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀ dáru nínú odò sì bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀ dáru."
  21,52,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: “Kí ni àwọn ère wọ̀nyí tí ẹ̀ ń dúró tì, tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún ṣe jẹ́ ná?”"
  21,53,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A bá àwọn bàbá wa tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún wọn ni.”"
  21,54,"Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin àti àwọn bàbá yín ti wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”"
  22,28,"nítorí kí wọ́n lè rí àwọn àǹfààní tó ń bẹ fún wọn àti nítorí kí wọ́n lè ṣèrántí orúkọ Allāhu fún àwọn ọjọ́ tí wọ́n ti mọ̀{1} lórí n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu pa lésè fún wọn nínú àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn. Nítorí náà, ẹ jẹ nínú rẹ̀, kí ẹ sì fi bọ́ aláìlera, tálíkà..",footnotes:1:[Ìyẹn àwọn ọjọ́ mẹ́wàá àkọ́kọ́ nínú oṣù Thul-hijjah.]
  22,29,"Lẹ́yìn náà, kí wọ́n yanjú ìdọ̀tí ara wọn fún ìparí iṣẹ́ Hajj wọn, kí wọ́n mú àwọn ẹ̀jẹ́ wọn ṣẹ, kí wọ́n sì yípo Ilé Láéláé náà."
  22,30,"Ìyẹn (nìyẹn). Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì pàtàkì àwọn n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu bu ọ̀wọ̀ fún, òhun ló lóore jùlọ fún un lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀. Wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn ní ẹ̀tọ́ fún yín àyàfi àwọn tí wọ́n ń kà (ní èèwọ̀) fún yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ jìnnà sí ẹ̀gbin òrìṣà. Kí ẹ sì jìnnà sí ọ̀rọ̀ irọ́."
  23,4,"àti àwọn tó ń ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ (ẹ̀mí àti ara) wọn.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún āyah yìí nìyí: “àti àwọn tó ń yọ zakāh”.]
  23,5,"àti àwọn tó ń ṣọ́ abẹ́ wọn,"
  23,6,"àfi ní ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ìyàwó wọn àti ẹrúbìnrin wọn. Dájúdájú wọn kì í ṣe ẹni èébú (tí wọ́n bá súnmọ́ wọn),"